    <string name="about_text"><![CDATA[
        <html>
        <meta content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" http-equiv=\"content-type\">
        <body>
        <h1>Welcome!</h1>
        <p>Simple and fast notepad for everyday</p>
        <h2>Tutorial</h2>
        <li><b>General</b>
        <p>All notes are saved in folder  <code>"Phone_storage/Notes/backup"</code> for access from every file manager or inner storage of device.</p>
        <p>Name of note is filename, so watch out when choose name for note. It should not contain illegal characters like - \\,/,ampersand,* etc.</p>
        </li>
        <li><b>Add note</b>
        <p>Press button "+" and fullfill name for note as filename.</p>
        <p>Fullfill description if desired.</p>
        </li>
        <li><b>Delete note</b>
            <p>Swipe left on note in list.</p>
            <p>After delete note will be placed in folder  <code>"Phone_storage/Notes/backup"</code>.</p>
        </li>
        <li><b>Edit note</b>
            <p>Press on note for editing</p>
        </li>
        <li><b>Show note in list</b>
            <p>Press show button in right conner of note</p>
        </li>
        </body>
        </html>
        ]]></string>
